<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> 96% of small businesses use social media. The ones that fail spread across 5 platforms and post inconsistently. Dominating 2 platforms beats being mediocre on 5.</p>
<p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> Companies that automate social media posting save more than 6 hours per week. A free tool like Buffer (3 channels, AI caption generation included) handles scheduling with zero cost.</p>
